                                    </div>
                                    <div class="modal-body">
                                        <p class="mb-4">{{ 'admin.shipping.index.808'|trans }}</p>
                                        <form class="mb-4">
                                            <div class="font-weight-bold mb-2">{{ 'admin.shipping.index.809'|trans }}</div>
                                            <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                                                <label class="form-check-label">
                                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="orderStatus" checked=""> {{ 'admin.shipping.index.810'|trans }}
                                                </label>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                                                <label class="form-check-label">
                                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="orderStatus"> {{ 'admin.shipping.index.811'|trans }}
                                                </label>
                                            </div>
                                        </form>
                                        <form>
                                            <div class="font-weight-bold mb-2">{{ 'admin.shipping.index.812'|trans }}</div>
                                            <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                                                <label class="form-check-label">
                                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="notificationMail" checked=""> {{ 'admin.shipping.index.813'|trans }}
                                                </label>
                                            </div>
                                        </form>
                                        <div class="d-inline-block" data-toggle="collapse" href="#viewEmail" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="viewEmail"><a><i class="fa fa-plus-square-o font-weight-bold mr-1"></i><span class="font-weight-bold">{{ 'admin.shipping.index.814'|trans }}</span></a></div>
                                        <div class="collapse bg-light p-4 ec-collapse bg-ec-formGray" id="viewEmail">
                                            {# TODO 発送お知らせメール表示 #}
                                            <p>[注文者名]様</p>
                                            <p>お客さまがご注文された以下の商品を発送いたしました。商品の到着まで、今しばらくお待ちくださいませ。</p>
